news.news: Bane (ankle) won't play Monday against the Mavericks.
news.analysis: Bane was considered doubtful leading up to Monday's clash due to a left ankle sprain, so this update arrives as expected. Look for Jaylen Wells, Luke Kennard and Jake LaRavia to get more looks in Bane's absence.
